Jab number yaad rakhna ho   → variable = 0  ==> ye marks aur Numbers ke liye use hota hai
Jab word yaad rakhna ho   → variable = ""   ==> jab ksis list me naam nikalna hota hai tab use karte hai(words) string/words/character ke liye use hota hai
Jab count karna ho          → variable = {}

Ek ek dekhna                → for loop
Check karna                 → if/else
Length nikalna              → len()
Even/Odd check              → % 2 == 0
